                                        &#10;Smite: C:\Users\XYZ\Documents\My Games\Smite\BattleGame\Config\BattleInput.ini
                                        &#10;TF2: C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\Team Fortress 2\tf\cfg\config.cfg"
